---
title: Sync Engine — Sequence Diagram
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant SE as Sync Engine
    participant SC as Smart Contract
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant FE as Frontend

    SE->>SC: On startup: getPhase(), candidateCount()
    SE->>DB: Clean stale candidates, backfill history

    loop Every 10 seconds
        SE->>SC: queryFilter (7 event types, batched 10 blocks)
        SC-->>SE: New events (candidates, votes, phases)
        SE->>SE: Dedup by txHash+logIndex
        SE->>DB: INSERT events, UPSERT candidates
        SE-->>FE: Socket.IO "blockchainEvent"

        SE->>SC: candidateCount(), getCandidate()
        SC-->>SE: Vote count changes
        alt Votes updated
            SE->>DB: UPDATE vote_count
            SE-->>FE: Socket.IO "voteUpdate"
        end

        SE->>SC: getPhase()
        alt Phase changed
            SE->>DB: snapshotResults() on end
            SE->>SC: rebuildMerkleTrees() on voting start
            SE-->>FE: Socket.IO "blockchainEvent"
        end
    end
